<i>Posted by Chromite on 10-06-2001 05:33 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>A little note about faction on this quest:<br />
<br />
If you or your guild is deciding to go to Claws of Veeshan faction I recommend you do a bit of killing in Skyshrine to get to amiably with the storm giants really quick.  Once you are at amiably, do this quest and then switch to Claws of Veeshan.  It's much easier to do it that way than to come back from being a Claws of Veeshan Ally and enemy #1 of Kromzek, of course.  <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt=""><FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
